00:41:22,710 --> 00:41:24,070
what exactly is the Storm Alliance?

692
00:41:24,070 --> 00:41:25,730
What kind of people are there?

693
00:41:25,880 --> 00:41:26,440
They're all

694
00:41:26,440 --> 00:41:28,240
