704
00:41:40,400 --> 00:41:42,020
So watch what you say,

705
00:41:42,110 --> 00:41:43,550
or they might decide to get rid of us.

706
00:41:43,550 --> 00:41:44,390
Y-Y-You're

707
00:41:44,590 --> 00:41:45,920
